			<p>"Everyone open your role card using the button at the bottom of your screen and review your character role. You will be playing from this character's perspective this round."</p>
		</blockquote>

	</div>

	{{!-- READ ROLES --}}
	<div class="screen">
		
		<section class="instruction decider">
			<h1>read the text in the blue box outloud</h1>
			<div>Once all players have introduced themselves, press next to continue</div>
		</section>
		<section class="instruction player">
			<h1>Open your Role Card and prepare to share</h1>
			<div>On your turn, read your character role title and bio outloud to the group.</div>
		</section>

		<blockquote class="speech decider form">
			"One at a time, go around the table introducing yourself by reading your character role title and short bio. Do not read your hidden agenda items outloud!"
			<button class="next-step submit" data-event="game:next_screen">next</button>
		</blockquote>
		<blockquote class="speech player">
			"One at a time, go around the table introducing yourself by reading your character role title and short bio. Do not read your hidden agenda items outloud!"
		</blockquote>

	</div>

	{{!-- AGENDA ITEMS --}}
	<div class="screen">
		
		<section class="instruction decider">
			<h1>read the text in the blue box outloud</h1>
			<div>Once everyone has had enough time to review their hidden agenda items, press next to continue.</div>
		</section>
		<section class="instruction player">
			<h1>Review your Hidden Agenda items</h1>
			<div>At the bottom of your role card are your hidden agenda items. Secretly review them now.</div>
		</section>

		<blockquote class="speech decider form">
			"Now everyone quietly review your hidden agenda items at the bottom of your role card. You’ll earn coins if they are included in the winning proposal. Keep them secret!"
			<button id="next" class="submit" data-event="game:next">next</button>
		</blockquote>
		<blockquote class="speech player">
